{"id":32,"date":"2013-11-30T00:00:00","date_gmt":"2013-11-29T16:00:00","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/ijz.me\/?p=32"},"modified":"2013-11-30T00:00:00","modified_gmt":"2013-11-29T16:00:00","slug":"linux%e4%b8%8b%e5%bd%bb%e5%ba%95%e5%88%a0%e9%99%a4oracle","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"http:\/\/ijz.me\/?p=32","title":{"rendered":"Linux\u4e0b\u5f7b\u5e95\u5220\u9664Oracle"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>1. \u7528 oracle \u7528\u6237\u767b\u5f55<\/p>\n<p>\u5982\u679c\u8981\u518d\u6b21\u5b89\u88c5\uff0c \u6700\u597d\u5148\u505a\u4e00\u4e9b\u5907\u4efd\u5de5\u4f5c\u3002<br \/>\n\u5305\u62ec\u7528\u6237\u7684\u767b\u5f55\u811a\u672c\uff0c\u6570\u636e\u5e93\u81ea\u52a8\u542f\u52a8\u5173\u95ed\u7684\u811a\u672c\uff0c\u548c Listener \u81ea\u52a8\u542f\u52a8\u7684\u811a\u672c\u3002<br \/>\n\u8981\u662f\u6709\u53ef\u80fd\u8fde\u521b\u5efa\u6570\u636e\u5e93\u7684\u811a\u672c\u4e5f\u4fdd\u5b58\u4e0b\u6765<\/p>\n<p>2. \u4f7f\u7528 SQL*PLUS \u505c\u6b62\u6570\u636e\u5e93<br \/>\n[oracle@ora920 oracle]$ sqlplus \/nolog<br \/>\nSQL&gt; connect \/ as sysdba<br \/>\nSQL&gt; shutdown<br \/>\nSQL&gt; exit<\/p>\n<p><!--more--><\/p>\n<p>3. \u505c\u6b62 Listener<br \/>\n[oracle@ora920 oracle]$ lsnrctl stop<\/p>\n<p>4. \u505c\u6b62 HTTP \u670d\u52a1<br \/>\n[oracle@ora920 oracle]$ $ORACLE_HOME\/Apache\/Apache\/bin\/apachectl stop<\/p>\n<p>5. \u7528 su \u6216\u8005\u91cd\u65b0\u767b\u5f55\u5230 root( \u5982\u60f3\u91cd\u65b0\u5b89\u88c5\u53ef\u4ee5\u4fdd\u7559 oracle \u7528\u6237\uff0c\u7701\u5f97\u8f93\u5165\u73af\u5883\u53d8\u91cf\u4e86 )<\/p>\n<p>6. \u5c06\u5b89\u88c5\u76ee\u5f55\u5220\u9664 # rm -rf \/opt\/oracle\/<\/p>\n<p>7. \u5c06 \/usr\/bin \u4e0b\u7684\u6587\u4ef6\u5220\u9664\u00a0# rm \/usr\/bin\/dbhome# rm \/usr\/bin\/oraenv<br \/>\n# rm \/usr\/bin\/coraenv<\/p>\n<p>8. \u5c06 \/etc\/oratab \u5220\u9664<br \/>\n# rm \/etc\/oratab<\/p>\n<p>9. \u5c06 \/etc\/oraInst.loc \u5220\u9664<br \/>\n# rm \/etc\/oraInst.loc<\/p>\n<p>10. \u5c06 oracle \u7528\u6237\u5220\u9664 ( \u82e5\u8981\u91cd\u65b0\u5b89\u88c5 , \u53ef\u4ee5\u4e0d\u5220\u9664 )<br \/>\n# userdel \u2013r oracle<\/p>\n<p>11. \u5c06\u7528\u6237\u7ec4\u5220\u9664 ( \u82e5\u8981\u91cd\u65b0\u5b89\u88c5 , \u53ef\u4ee5\u4e0d\u5220\u9664 )<br \/>\n# groupdel oinstall<br \/>\n# groupdel dba<\/p>\n<p>12. \u5c06\u542f\u52a8\u670d\u52a1\u5220\u9664<br \/>\n# chkconfig &#8211;del dbora<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>1. \u7528 oracle \u7528\u6237\u767b\u5f55 \u5982\u679c\u8981\u518d\u6b21\u5b89\u88c5\uff0c \u6700\u597d\u5148\u505a\u4e00\u4e9b\u5907\u4efd\u5de5\u4f5c\u3002 \u5305\u62ec\u7528\u6237\u7684\u767b\u5f55\u811a\u672c\uff0c\u6570\u636e\u5e93\u81ea\u52a8\u542f\u52a8 [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[20],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-32","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-oracle"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/ijz.me\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts\/32","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/ijz.me\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/ijz.me\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/ijz.me\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/ijz.me\/index.php?rest_route=%2Fwp%2Fv2%2Fcomments&post=32"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/ijz.me\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts\/32\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/ijz.me\/index.php?rest_route=%2Fwp%2Fv2%2Fmedia&parent=32"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/ijz.me\/index.php?rest_route=%2Fwp%2Fv2%2Fcategories&post=32"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/ijz.me\/index.php?rest_route=%2Fwp%2Fv2%2Ftags&post=32"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templa